WEBVTT

00:02:29.687 --> 00:02:31.572
a bus with 80 passengers

00:02:31.572 --> 00:02:34.301
has a right to 80 times more road space

00:02:34.301 --> 00:02:37.173
than a car with one.

00:02:37.173 --> 00:02:41.566
We have been so used to inequality, sometimes,

00:02:41.566 --> 00:02:45.297
that it's before our noses and we do not see it.

00:02:45.297 --> 00:02:47.573
Less than 100 years ago,

00:02:47.573 --> 00:02:48.960
women could not vote,

00:02:48.960 --> 00:02:51.166
and it seemed normal,

00:02:51.166 --> 00:02:54.850
in the same way that it seems normal today

00:02:54.850 --> 00:02:57.782
to see a bus in traffic.

